"      Hou S. Expanding the kidney donor pool: ethical and medical considerations. Kidney Int 2000; 58:1820.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?29/62/30697/abstract/3\">",
"      Ellison MD, McBride MA, Taranto SE, et al. Living kidney donors in need of kidney transplants: a report from the organ procurement and transplantation network. Transplantation 2002; 74:1349.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?29/62/30697/abstract/4\">",
"      Davis CL. Evaluation of the living kidney donor: current perspectives. Am J Kidney Dis 2004; 43:508.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
